(Explore BIL:  Bridge Notes - Teachers:   Paulg: ) 
Paul also keeps one of the most active bridge blogs and provides regular updates on his on-line and off-line adventures. Check it out at           ^*Hwww.thebeercard.blogspot.com ^*N   

